  "instructions": [
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the sliced bell pepper and carrots and cook until tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped bean sprouts and cooked chickpeas and stir-fry for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "Add the cooked rice vermicelli noodles and stir-fry until heated through.",
